nodes.text: Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II Collector's Edition digital art book

A digital art book was released with the Collector's Edition of the video game Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II in 2010 that contained a game script and behind-the-scenes information on the game and its development. It was released in a collectible USB flash drive toy known as a Mimobot that was shaped like the character Starkiller.
